<lyrics>[V1]
 1. I van Khawpiu thak nuom tak achun,
 Ziechun hukhin te kituok hitiu;
 I lungkham nau cheng bei zo ta'n a,
 Kumsawt chawlhna In I tun tieng leh.

[V2]
 Aw Eden, Khawpi thak,
 Ma a sanga nuom zaw;
 Ziechun kumsawt in chawl zing tai tiu,
 I Lalpau khawpi sat thak akhun.

[V3]
 2. Zie van Khawpi nawpna mun achun,
 Zie khawvel hi I taihsan tieng leh;
 Mi thiengtho tung masate haw tawh,
 I Lalpau ma ah kituok hitiu.

[V4]
 3. Ziechun mi thiengtho tamtak a um,
 Thiemgau, martar, hukdamte cheng tawh;
 Naupang hukdama um te cheng tawh,
 Tun Khawpi hawih akhun la a sau.

[V5]
 4. Van Khawlai sana tuia luon tawh,
 Lalpa Pathien kumsawt a vak tawh;
 Angel vam leh In vak lopi tawh,
 Hukhinte cheng mel muh ka ngaklah.</lyrics>
<title>IN EDEN ABOVE</title>
</song>